{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotations"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"array must conform to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"removeAnnotations:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotations:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1833","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"}},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations in the array."}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotations:":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"removeAnnotations:","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations in the array.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}]}}}